text.tspan: 1 M Monitor for silence, m Monitor for activity
2 D Detach other clients, d detach from session

g.aria-label: CTRL-e Open .tmux.conf in your $EDITOR CTRL-r Reload .tmux.conf CTRL-o Swap active pane with next one CTRL-x Kill windows except current one CTRL-u Merge this session with another CTRL-s Toggle status bar visibility CTRL- Resize Pane
